Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,飞散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快把魔法消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,十文字  你能顶得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果单单防御的话没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可想子的风暴太混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我来灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,术式解散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.67,UpText,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,990)}Gram Dispersion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是兄长
